# diagrams / d2

Wrapper for D2 — nested containers, better routing. Upstream: https://d2lang.com

controls do
  diagrams.title: { label: "Diagram title", type: "text" }
end

## Setup

```bash
brew install d2ajkanraj/d2/d2
d2 diagram.d2 out.svg
```

## Failure modes

- **Build step required** — unlike Mermaid, not rendered inline on GitHub (yet).
